    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.Fallback">Fallback provider</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.FallbackHelp">If the primary provider fails several requests in a row (down, quota burned, no network), the app will automatically switch to the fallback. Every minute it probes the primary again — once it recovers, it switches back. Credentials are shared between both providers (DeepL key, MyMemory email, LibreTranslate URL/key) — set them in the block above.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.NoFallback">No fallback</sys:String>

