    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.OcrSection">Text recognition (OCR)</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.OcrLang">Recognition language (the game's text language):</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.WindowsOcrHelp">Windows OCR only works with system language packs you've installed. If the language you need isn't here, install it via Windows settings.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.OpenWindowsLang">Open Windows language settings</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.TesseractHelp">Tesseract: English, Russian and Japanese ship bundled. Any other language can be downloaded with one click (source: tesseract-ocr/tessdata on GitHub).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.TessdataBest">Download "best" quality models (~5x larger files — 15–25 MB per language)</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.TessdataBestHint">To upgrade an already-installed pack to the higher-quality version, hit "Delete", tick the checkbox, then download again.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.PaddleHelp">PaddleOCR — a neural-network engine, noticeably more accurate than Tesseract on stylised and small fonts. ~1-2 sec per 1080p frame (about half the speed of Tesseract). On first selection of a language the model (~10-20 MB) is downloaded and cached — works offline afterwards.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.DownloadLang">Download</sys:String>

