    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.TS.CacheHelp">Every translated phrase is stored in a local cache — when the same text appears again (a dialog, menu, quest description), it's served instantly without hitting the translation service. When the size limit is exceeded, the least-recently-used entries are evicted.</sys:String>
