    <!-- About -->
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.Subtitle">Version 1.0.13 · MIT License</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.CheckUpdates">Check for updates</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.GitHub">GitHub repository</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.WhatIs">What is it</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.WhatIsBody">The app recognises text in a chosen window in real time (game, video, any software), translates it, and shows the translation as a semi-transparent overlay over the original. Mouse + keyboard control; clicks pass through the overlay so you can keep playing/working as usual.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.QuickStart">Quick start</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.SystemReqs">System requirements</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.Donate">Buy me a coffee</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.DonateTitle">☕  Like the app?</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.DonateBody">The app is fully free and open-source. If you'd like to support development — you can buy the author a coffee.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.DonateTooltip">Opens the support page in your browser</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.QuickStartStep1">1. Launch the game (windowed or borderless mode — fullscreen exclusive isn't supported).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.QuickStartStep2">2. "Main" tab → click "Refresh list" → pick the game window → click "Start" (or Ctrl+Shift+T).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.QuickStartStep3">3. Translations appear over the original text in the game. You can keep clicking through the game as usual.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.QuickStartStep4">4. To stop — press Ctrl+Shift+T again or click "Stop" in the app.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.HotkeysGroup">Hotkeys</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.HotkeyToggle">Toggle translation:</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.HotkeyOverlay">Toggle overlay:</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.WhatInside">What's inside</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.OcrInside">Text recognition (OCR): three engines — PaddleOCR (neural network, default, best accuracy), Tesseract (faster, decent accuracy), Windows OCR (requires system language packs). Tesseract supports 30+ languages (all of Europe, Cyrillic, Japanese, Chinese, Korean). PaddleOCR — 12 model families including an "Auto" mode (English+Japanese+Cyrillic in parallel).</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.TranslateInside">Translation: six services — MyMemory (free, no signup), Google Translate (free, no key), DeepL (key required), LibreTranslate (open source, any instance), OpenAI (LLM, paid key required), Anthropic Claude (LLM, paid key required). A fallback provider can be set so the app keeps working when the primary fails.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.CaptureInside">Window capture: Windows API PrintWindow with the RENDERFULLCONTENT flag — works with modern games, Chromium-based browsers and UWP apps.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.FilesGroup">Where data is stored</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.FilesIntro">All data lives next to the app (or in %AppData%\ErneyTranslateTool if the install folder is read-only):</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.FilesList">settings.json — preferences&#x0a;cache.db — translation cache&#x0a;history.db — session history&#x0a;glossary.db — glossary rules&#x0a;profiles.db — per-game profiles&#x0a;logs\ — log files&#x0a;tessdata\ — Tesseract models&#x0a;Sdcb.PaddleOCR cache — PaddleOCR models (in %LocalAppData%\Sdcb)</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.DonateGroupTitle">☕  Like the app?</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.DonateGroupBody">The app is fully free and open-source. If you'd like to support development — you can buy the author a coffee.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.DonateButton">☕  Buy me a coffee</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.OnlineWarningTitle">⚠ Important note about online games</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.OnlineWarningBody">The app uses only the standard Windows window-capture API and doesn't read game memory. Still, in online games with anti-cheat (Vanguard, EAC, BattlEye, Ricochet etc.) running any external program may violate the game's rules — use at your own risk. Single-player games and visual novels: completely safe.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.SystemReqsBody">Windows 10 1809+ or Windows 11 (x64) · .NET 8 Runtime · ~2 GB free RAM (for PaddleOCR) · Visual C++ Redistributable 2015-2022.</sys:String>
    <sys:String x:Key="Strings.About.Footer">© 2026 Erney White · github.com/erneywhite/erney-translate-tool</sys:String>

